{"tid":633984,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞]《留》[原曲：薛之謙－我害怕]","createTime":"2018-04-18T19:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T07:16:23.000Z","uid":108844,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c063c89208325e1de4e300bf65095beaf729359c","tid":633984,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:17:31.000Z","msg":"原曲：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W36xriMOgP8?t=2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW36xriMOgP8%3Ft%3D2s&d=E9NX38uQGjLoXYwlvE02WghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=12222276\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/W36xriMOgP8?t=2s</a><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n大家好，又係我龜仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n失眠嘅人通常都特別多嘢諗，而失眠嘅毒撚諗嘅嘢就更加痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼上次ff個女朋友出嚟俾自己諗點同佢求婚之後，今次我ff咗個死咗嘅女朋友出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果另一半離開咗哩個世界，你會點樣消沈？消沈幾耐？<br />\n佢同你嘅回憶又可以點樣保存？<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n《留》<br />\n<br />\n留低當天那戲飛 留日後用來念記<br />\n留起你做過的 每本筆記<br />\n<br />\n留守於這個廢墟 凝望陌路來又去<br />\n留不到逝去的你 哪怕聽到一句<br />\n<br />\n留聲機不會說穿 時日默默來奉勸<br />\n留心聽舊唱片 老化了怎轉<br />\n<br />\n留戀班房裡桌椅 螢幕上動人大志<br />\n留戀課後你忽爾 要吻我一次<br />\n<br />\n沒有詩 形容當中故事<br />\n誰在意 呼吸都帶根刺<br />\n沒法子 誰明當中意義<br />\n痛心時 我會淚流不已<br />\n<br />\n(留不低 留不低 留不低)<br />\n<br />\n留一杯清澈暖水 如服藥便能飲醉<br />\n如果哪日我走了 你會否心碎<br />\n<br />\n留宿於街角安睡 唯望在淡然夜裡<br />\n留心聽著你呼叫 你帶我歸去<br />\n<br />\n沒有詩 描繪出故事<br />\n還在意 願你在天會知<br />\n沒法子 誰明當中意義<br />\n再有心儀 盼你默許一次<br />\n<br />\n留多一天便放手 人活著為誰消瘦<br />\n留不到是你傾心過 的深秋<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">其他改詞傳送門：<br />\n[改詞] [已唱]《最痛中經過》 [原曲：全世界誰傾聽你]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/632169/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/632169/page/1</a><br />\n[改詞]《星宿》[原曲: 追光者]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/625629/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/625629/page/1</a><br />\n[改詞][龜仔你出夠post未] 《目送》[原曲: 體面]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/626428/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/626428/page/1</a><br />\n[改詞][想求婚嘅巴打可能啱用]《我願意》[原曲：這就是愛情]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/629594/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/629594/page/1</a><br />\n</span>-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"fb8b7a8cc6b3e71effd7baa3dad0af674303f6e7","tid":633984,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:22:38.000Z","msg":"眼瞓了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef08a6639ac36b1f7790c6714aabe84decaccdbd","tid":633984,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T00:47:53.000Z","msg":"早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0fbcdcb4e843cb7eb42d7a39f0169ff9ba5205","tid":633984,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T01:04:26.000Z","msg":"無限子孫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e065b4ac14757ae114e9320b2720158e7ac314b","tid":633984,"uid":100230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T02:27:49.000Z","msg":"正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb79c023a77b7c29a34740b95e7857783c30cbf","tid":633984,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed0fbcdcb4e843cb7eb42d7a39f0169ff9ba5205","tid":633984,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T01:04:26.000Z","msg":"無限子孫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T04:50:54.000Z","msg":"全靠ff<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/